[0.000, "o", "\u001b[1;34mof structure to be penetrated in order to get to a simple scalar where simple means non-nested.\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[0m"]
[0.001, "o", "\u001b[1;34mThe depth of an array is 1 greater than that of its most deeply nested item.\r\n"]
